{"tid":1990031,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我配咗條白雪公主請大家「登記做選民」！！","createTime":"2020-04-26T11:43:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T09:22:23.000Z","uid":217060,"like":121,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"34a14891b169b98a21354905e4623c8944dffaea","tid":1990031,"uid":217060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"雖然自己放上連登有點柒(要好大勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>經朋友鼓勵之後決定放上嚟！如果可以多一個人因此做選民，柒又何妨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n就算呢個post冇人理我都好想請大家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5月2前登記做選民！登記做選民！</span></strong><br />\n<strong>我知道大家覺得好無助，但盡做好嗎？</strong><br />\n<strong>睇下身邊有冇小朋友7月25號或之前滿18歲，叫佢做選民呀</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>另外身為外國L，希望9月搞得掂肺炎大家一齊返屋企投票</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解放上嚟，係因為某日上連登有個post「登記做選民」改歌得到啟發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以條片最尾我續寫咗首歌<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><em>[size=2]登記做選民，登記做選民<br />\n好快截止，其實有網址可以去左先<br />\n登記做選民，只要為了香港多一票<br />\n立法會選舉等你投票[/size=1]</em></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/1L80JLXPYas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F1L80JLXPYas&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=6b4bab1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/1L80JLXPYas</a><br />\n　<br />\n無論地方選區定功能界別，<span style=\"color: red;\">即上</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都可睇下自己係咪已經登記咗<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo-form.gov.hk%2Feto%2Fch%2Findex.jsp&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=5a7c9b41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo-form.gov.hk/eto/ch/index.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n其他系列未能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/EhGF3Qd2Xa8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FEhGF3Qd2Xa8&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=be448b15\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/EhGF3Qd2Xa8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ruKB9BSB1fQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FruKB9BSB1fQ&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=323d6f28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ruKB9BSB1fQ</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/VzRfoo68oJY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FVzRfoo68oJY&d=LcLc405txlysKZNFfpEZ4GlERb1kSGFVDbesiz0gOXg%3D&h=ab31d344\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/VzRfoo68oJY</a>"},{"pid":"c593ddbd2782db8eb9d956ddf865a29a0f1537bc","tid":1990031,"uid":217060,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34a14891b169b98a21354905e4623c8944dffaea","tid":1990031,"uid":217060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-26T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"雖然自己放上連登有點柒(要好大勇氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>經朋友鼓勵之後決定放上嚟！如果可以多一個人因此做選民，柒又何妨？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span><br />\n就算呢個post冇人理我都好想請大家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5月2前登記做選民！登記做選民！</span></strong><br />\n<strong>我知道大家覺得好無助，但盡做好嗎？</strong><br />\n<strong>睇下身邊有冇小朋友7月25號或之前滿18歲，叫佢做選民呀</strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>另外身為外國L，希望9月搞得掂肺炎大家一齊返屋企投票</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解放上嚟，係因為某日上連登有個post「登記做選民」改歌得到啟發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以條片最尾我續寫咗首歌<br />\n<span style=\"color: navy;\"><em>[size=2]登記做選民，登記做選民<br />\n好快截止，其實有網址可以去左先<br 